<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 22:06:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡的双手沾满了我家人的鲜血”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-familys-blood-is-on-netanyahus-hands/0000018b-a633-dc41-af9f-ef33c9170000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 21:53:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-familys-blood-is-on-netanyahus-hands/0000018b-a633-dc41-af9f-ef33c9170000</guid></item><item><title>柏林“停止种族灭绝”血腥诽谤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/berlins-stop-the-genocide-blood-libel/0000018b-a633-dc41-af9f-ef33d07a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 21:44:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/berlins-stop-the-genocide-blood-libel/0000018b-a633-dc41-af9f-ef33d07a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列向拜登政府承诺，美国步枪不会流向约旦河西岸定居者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-promises-biden-administration-that-u-s-rifles-guns-wont-go-to-west-bank-settlers/0000018b-a668-dc0b-a1cb-e7ee85860000</link><description>以色列作出保证之际，美国政府和国会对约旦河西岸定居者领导的针对巴勒斯坦人的暴力行为日益增多感到担忧</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 21:24:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-promises-biden-administration-that-u-s-rifles-guns-wont-go-to-west-bank-settlers/0000018b-a668-dc0b-a1cb-e7ee85860000</guid></item><item><title>美国向中东派遣携带战斧导弹的攻击潜艇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sends-attack-submarine-with-tomahawk-missiles-to-middle-east/0000018b-a605-d9c0-a5fb-ef5d7b330000</link><description>佛罗里达号航空母舰周日通过苏伊士运河，加入红海艾森豪威尔号航空母舰领导的打击群。拜登政府官员向伊朗和真主党暗示，如果他们袭击以色列，美国准备采取军事行动</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 21:16:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sends-attack-submarine-with-tomahawk-missiles-to-middle-east/0000018b-a605-d9c0-a5fb-ef5d7b330000</guid></item><item><title>承认以色列人质家属为恐怖主义受害者的法律颁布</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/law-recognizing-israeli-hostages-families-as-terrorism-victims-is-enacted/0000018b-a655-d9c0-a5fb-ef5d4cab0000</link><description>紧急法案每季度为家庭提供 90,000 谢克尔，并包括承认人质或失踪人员的 LGBTQ 伴侣</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 21:15:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/law-recognizing-israeli-hostages-families-as-terrorism-victims-is-enacted/0000018b-a655-d9c0-a5fb-ef5d4cab0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称并未袭击加沙的希法医院，否认哈马斯的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article-live/jordan-our-air-force-dropped-aid-into-gaza-u-s-deploys-nuclear-submarine-to-middle-east/0000018b-a261-dc41-af9f-eb632d730006</link><description>以色列国防军称下午从黎巴嫩发射了 30 枚火箭弹；哈马斯声称对海法地区 18 人枪击事件负责 ■ 边境警察在耶路撒冷袭击中丧生 ■ 巴勒斯坦活动家阿赫德·塔米米因涉嫌煽动而被捕 ■ 10 月 7 日哈马斯大屠杀中至少有 1,300 名平民和士兵丧生，其中 241 名人质在加沙被扣，40 名人质被扣押。下落不明 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：超过 10,000 人死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 20:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article-live/jordan-our-air-force-dropped-aid-into-gaza-u-s-deploys-nuclear-submarine-to-middle-east/0000018b-a261-dc41-af9f-eb632d730006</guid></item><item><title>“哈马斯无法统治加沙：”欧盟主席提出以色列与哈马斯战争后的路线图</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-06/ty-article/hamas-cannot-govern-gaza-eu-chief-presents-roadmap-for-after-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-a5bf-d9c0-a5fb-edff13d10000</link><description>乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩表示，以色列与哈马斯战争结束后的道路可能包括一支“联合国授权的国际和平部队”，并呼吁立即释放加沙的所有人质</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 19:32:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-06/ty-article/hamas-cannot-govern-gaza-eu-chief-presents-roadmap-for-after-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-a5bf-d9c0-a5fb-edff13d10000</guid></item><item><title>叶史瓦大学向受到反犹太主义威胁的教授提供职位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/yeshiva-university-to-offer-positions-to-professors-threatened-by-antisemitism/0000018b-a5b9-da24-a1cb-b7fd5b830000</link><description>纽约叶史瓦大学商学院院长向美国的犹太和以色列教授发出呼吁，他们发现自己处于“敌对环境”中，可能有兴趣访问教职至少一个学期</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 18:11:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/yeshiva-university-to-offer-positions-to-professors-threatened-by-antisemitism/0000018b-a5b9-da24-a1cb-b7fd5b830000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的极右翼部长是给哈马斯的礼物</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-06/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-far-right-ministers-are-a-gift-to-hamas/0000018b-a5bc-dc0b-a1cb-e5fe57210000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡知道，他的极右翼部长（其中一些人将核弹作为加沙的“选择”）对以色列不利。但一如既往，他将自己的政治需要和个人利益置于任何其他考虑之上</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 18:09:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-06/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-far-right-ministers-are-a-gift-to-hamas/0000018b-a5bc-dc0b-a1cb-e5fe57210000</guid></item><item><title>德国记者被以色列士兵拘留：“用枪指着我们并问我们是否是犹太人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/german-journalists-detained-by-israeli-soldiers-asked-if-we-were-jewish-at-gunpoint/0000018b-a5ae-d9c0-a5fb-edfee9ed0000</link><description>士兵们在西岸希伯伦以南拘留了德国公共广播公司 ARD 的记者，该团队正在报道极端主义定居者的暴力行为。以色列军队：“以色列国防军对造成的任何不便表示歉意”</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 18:04:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/german-journalists-detained-by-israeli-soldiers-asked-if-we-were-jewish-at-gunpoint/0000018b-a5ae-d9c0-a5fb-edfee9ed0000</guid></item><item><title>“这是非常个人化的”：10 月 7 日，以色列士兵在加沙内部生活发生了改变</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-11-06/ty-article-podcast/its-very-personal-inside-gaza-with-the-israeli-soldiers-whose-lives-changed-on-oct-7/0000018b-a559-d9c0-a5fb-ed59e9f20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 17:21:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-11-06/ty-article-podcast/its-very-personal-inside-gaza-with-the-israeli-soldiers-whose-lives-changed-on-oct-7/0000018b-a559-d9c0-a5fb-ed59e9f20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称在约旦河西岸击毙了四名恐怖分子，其中包括哈马斯和法塔赫成员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-killed-four-terrorists-including-hamas-fatah-members-in-west-bank/0000018b-a580-dc0b-a1cb-e5c681d30000</link><description>据以色列称，两名被杀的哈马斯和法塔赫成员对数十起枪击事件负责，并计划在以色列境内进行更多枪击事件</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 17:19:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-killed-four-terrorists-including-hamas-fatah-members-in-west-bank/0000018b-a580-dc0b-a1cb-e5c681d30000</guid></item><item><title>作家指责以色列在加沙实施“种族灭绝”后，耶路撒冷顶级剧院冻结了演出</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/top-jerusalem-theater-freezes-production-after-writer-accuses-israel-of-genocide-in-gaza/0000018b-a584-dc0b-a1cb-e5c655550000</link><description>英国裔阿富汗人哈米德·阿米里（Hamed Amiri）在社交媒体上发布了反对以色列的言论，他撰写了戏剧《有两颗心的男孩》的回忆录。可汗剧院表示避免艺术审查，但不会容忍“煽动”恐怖主义</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 16:59:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/top-jerusalem-theater-freezes-production-after-writer-accuses-israel-of-genocide-in-gaza/0000018b-a584-dc0b-a1cb-e5c655550000</guid></item><item><title>德国媒体敦促在加沙战争期间坚定支持以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/german-language-press-urges-unwavering-support-for-israel-during-gaza-war/0000018b-a4be-dc41-af9f-efbe19e20000</link><description>在以色列和哈马斯之间的战争尚未结束的情况下，面对越来越大规模的要求停火的集会，德国、奥地利和瑞士媒体形成统一战线，敦促加大对以色列的支持</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 16:37:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/german-language-press-urges-unwavering-support-for-israel-during-gaza-war/0000018b-a4be-dc41-af9f-efbe19e20000</guid></item><item><title>加沙哈马斯卫生部：自战争开始以来已有逾万人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/hamas-health-ministry-in-gaza-more-than-10-000-have-been-killed-there-since-the-war-began/0000018b-a541-da24-a1cb-b74d53b40000</link><description>据该部称，70%以上的死者是妇女、儿童和老人；超过24,000人受伤；医生被迫在没有麻醉的情况下进行手术</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 16:27:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/hamas-health-ministry-in-gaza-more-than-10-000-have-been-killed-there-since-the-war-began/0000018b-a541-da24-a1cb-b74d53b40000</guid></item><item><title>南非召回驻特拉维夫特使，指责以色列在加沙实施“种族灭绝”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/asia-and-australia/2023-11-06/ty-article/south-africa-recalls-ambassador-in-tel-aviv-over-israeli-genocide-in-gaza/0000018b-a528-dc0b-a1cb-e5eeab060000</link><description>比勒陀利亚还威胁要对以色列大使采取行动，因为他批评以色列对战争的立场。南非与约旦、土耳其、玻利维亚和智利等其他国家一起对以色列采取类似的外交行动</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 16:18:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/asia-and-australia/2023-11-06/ty-article/south-africa-recalls-ambassador-in-tel-aviv-over-israeli-genocide-in-gaza/0000018b-a528-dc0b-a1cb-e5eeab060000</guid></item><item><title>欧洲野猫冷落家猫2000年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2023-11-06/ty-article/wildcats-in-europe-snubbed-domestic-cats-for-2-000-years/0000018b-a516-d9c0-a5fb-ed5e1e760000</link><description>直到 20 世纪 50 年代，苏格兰野猫队也一直坚守着抵抗入侵者的立场，那么后来发生了什么变化呢？</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 16:00:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2023-11-06/ty-article/wildcats-in-europe-snubbed-domestic-cats-for-2-000-years/0000018b-a516-d9c0-a5fb-ed5e1e760000</guid></item><item><title>35个以色列犹太和阿拉伯权利团体呼吁停火、人质交易、政治解决冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-human-rights-orgs-call-for-ceasefire-hostage-deal-political-solution-to-conflict/0000018b-a53a-da24-a1cb-b77e8a860000</link><description>这些组织签署的一封公开信还呼吁以色列遏制西岸猖獗的定居者暴力，停止迫害以色列的巴勒斯坦公民以及那些声援加沙居民并反对战争的人</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 15:52:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-human-rights-orgs-call-for-ceasefire-hostage-deal-political-solution-to-conflict/0000018b-a53a-da24-a1cb-b77e8a860000</guid></item><item><title>这些是伊朗从也门向以色列发射的导弹和无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/these-are-the-iranian-rockets-and-drones-launched-at-israel-from-yemen/0000018b-a45b-dc41-af9f-ef7bcc800000</link><description>以色列、美国甚至沙特都在红海地区部署导弹防御系统，以挫败伊朗支持的也门胡塞政权的袭击</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 15:44:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/these-are-the-iranian-rockets-and-drones-launched-at-israel-from-yemen/0000018b-a45b-dc41-af9f-ef7bcc800000</guid></item><item><title>支持乌克兰？然后支持以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/support-ukraine-then-support-israel/0000018b-a4dd-da24-a1cb-b7ddf6f30000</link><description>乌克兰和以色列都面临着具有明显种族灭绝意图、使用恐怖主义和犯下危害人类罪的敌人。简而言之，如果俄罗斯获胜，乌克兰人就会消失。如果哈马斯获胜，以色列人就会消失</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 15:33:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/support-ukraine-then-support-israel/0000018b-a4dd-da24-a1cb-b7ddf6f30000</guid></item></channel></rss>